text: Jennifer Cerqueira Veloso (born 18 January 2000), known as Jennifer Cerqueira, is an Andorran footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Andorra women's national team. ==Career== Cerqueira has been capped for the Andorra national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers Category:Andorran people of Portuguese descent
